msgctxt "an2.280-309:281.1.4"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, dve atthavase paṭicca tathāgatena sāvakānaṃ "
"tiṇavatthārako paññatto”ti. (11–300.)"
msgstr ""
"These are the two reasons why the Realized One laid down the settlement of a "
"disciplinary matter by covering over with grass for his disciples.”"

